  "texts": [
    "Following quality control with FastQC 104, Illumina short reads were trimmed using Trimmomatic v.0.36 (ref.",
    "91) and mapped on the C. arabica reference assembly with BWA-MEM v.0.7.16a-r1181 (ref. 105).",
    "For the Linnaean sample, the reads were processed according to the protocols recommended for degraded DNA analysis in MapDamage v.2.0.8 (ref. 106).",
    "GATK (v.3.8.0) pipeline was used for SNP calling.",
    "Duplicates were marked and removed using Picard v.2.0.1 and genotype likelihoods were called into GVCF files using HaplotypeCaller (GATK)."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}